# Docker Integration & Shop Design Walkthrough

I have successfully integrated Docker and synchronized the Shop design with the Landing page.

## Changes Overview

### 1. Docker Integration
- **Containerized App**: Custom [Dockerfile](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Dockerfile) with multi-stage build (Node.js -> Nginx).
- **Orchestration**: [docker-compose.yml](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/docker-compose.yml) mapping port 8080:80.
- **Optimization**: [.dockerignore](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/.dockerignore) and Nginx Gzip compression.

### 2. Shop Design Overhaul
- **Dark Theme**: Switched [Shop.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Shop.tsx) from Light Mode to Dark Mode (`#020617`) to match [Landing.tsx](file:///c:/Users/Adonis/Downloads/landing-page---v3/Landing.tsx).
- **Liquid Glass Aesthetic**: Implemented glassmorphism on the Navbar and Product Cards.
- **Animation**: Added the same background animations (floating blobs, scanning beam) as the Landing page.
- **Consistency**: Unified color palette ("Cream Cyan") and typography.

## How to Run

1.  **Build and Start:**
    ```bash
    docker compose up -d --build
    ```

2.  **Access the Application:**
    - Local: [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080)
    - Mobile/Network: **[http://192.168.1.165:8080](http://192.168.1.165:8080)**

3.  **Stop:**
    ```bash
    docker compose down
    ```
